android.support.v4.app

Interface SupportActivity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SherlockActivity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceptFriendActivity, AddressBookPicker, AppCorralActivity, BootstrapActivity, ClaimKeyActivity, EmailUnclaimedMembersActivity, FeedDetailsActivity, FeedIdentityGrid, FeedListActivity, FeedPannerActivity, FragmentActivity, ImageGalleryActivity, MembersActivity, MusubiBaseActivity, NearbyActivity, PhotoEditorActivity, PickContactsActivity, PickFeedActivity, RelationshipsActivity, SendContentActivity, SettingsActivity, SketchWrapperActivity, ViewProfileActivity, WebAppActivity

    public interface SupportActivity
extends SherlockActivity

    Instances of this interface represent an activity provided by the support library (e.g., FragmentActivity).

    Provided are all of the methods which would be available if you were accessing the underlying activity directly and you can safely assume that any instances of this interface can be cast to an Activity. It is preferred, however, that you call asActivity() instead.
